sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Child/Parent)
    participant FE as Frontend (Flutter)
    participant API as Task API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant BullMQ as BullMQ Queue
    participant Notif as Notification Service
    participant PrefWorker as Preferred Time Worker
    participant UserDB as User Collection

    Note over U,UserDB: 📅 SCENARIO 1: Get Suggestion (Before Task Creation)
    U->>FE: Tap "Scheduled Time" field
    FE->>API: GET /tasks/suggest-preferred-time?assignedUserId=XXX
    API->>UserDB: Get user's preferredTime
    UserDB-->>API: preferredTime: "08:17"
    API-->>FE: Suggestion: { time: "08:17", explanation: "..." }
    FE->>U: Show suggestion dialog
    U->>FE: Accept or choose custom time

    Note over U,UserDB: 📝 SCENARIO 2: Create Task with Scheduled Time
    U->>FE: Fill task form with scheduledTime
    FE->>API: POST /tasks { scheduledTime: "08:17", ... }
    API->>DB: Validate & create task
    DB-->>API: Task created
    API->>Redis: Invalidate cache
    Redis-->>API: Cache invalidated
    API-->>FE: Task created ✓

    Note over U,UserDB: ✅ SCENARIO 3: Complete Task (Triggers Calculation)
    U->>API: PUT /tasks/:id/status (complete task)
    API->>DB: Validate & update task status
    DB-->>API: Task completed
    API->>Redis: Invalidate task cache
    Redis-->>API: Cache invalidated
    API-->>U: Task completed ✓

    Note over API,BullMQ: Trigger preferred time calculation
    API->>BullMQ: Add job: calculatePreferredTime
    BullMQ-->>API: Job queued

    Note over BullMQ: Async processing
    BullMQ->>PrefWorker: Process job
    PrefWorker->>DB: Get last 10 completed tasks
    DB-->>PrefWorker: Tasks with startTime
    PrefWorker->>PrefWorker: Calculate average start time
    PrefWorker->>UserDB: Update user.preferredTime
    UserDB-->>PrefWorker: Preferred time updated
    PrefWorker-->>BullMQ: Job completed

    Note over U,UserDB: 🔄 Next task scheduled at updated preferred time
